        h1 Call for Speakers

        p Nodesconf London is a one-day, single-track conference.

        p We'll bring together our industry's enterprise heavyweights, our subject experts and highlight the finest talent London has to offer.  We’ll be bringing you perspectives from the enterprise whilst providing cutting edge developer insights.

        p If you'd like to be involved, we'd love to hear your proposal, even if you have never spoken at a conference before, so get in touch!

        h2 Format & Topics

        p Talks will be 20 minutes long, followed by a Q&A Panel with time for questions. Our panel host will conduct an intimate discussion, actively involving the audience and our speakers, offering participants a more in-depth opportunity to learn.

