        h4 Leave at home:

        ul.talkuntopics
          li: span Library specific talks
          li: span Your company's new product

        p It's best to prepare for no internet and we ask all speakers to read and comply with our code of conduct.

        h2 Our Promise

        p We treat all speakers same and understand the commitment you are making to Nodeconf London, so, here is our promise to you.

        h3 Reimbursement

        p We'll pay you £250 and You'll receive a complimentary ticket to the next Nodeconf London! Want to waive some, or all of your fee? we'll make a donation to our chosen non-profit.

        h3 We've got you covered!

        p We'll cover the cost of your travel including the cost of your flights, and if you like, we'll make your travel arrangements on your behalf. We will also be on hand to help you with your needs in and around the conference.

        p We'll cover the cost of your accommodation. If you want to stay a little extra day, we will do our best to accommodate. Please let us know if you have any accessibility considerations.

        p On the day of the conference and the day before, we'll provide you with breakfast, lunch and £25! If you need some mobile data, we'll have some pre-loaded mifi devices ready to go.

        p If your company is able to cover any your expenses, we'll list them as a sponsor.

        h2 Let's go?

        p Whether this is your first proposal or whether your a seasoned pro, we'll do our best to help you shape your talk to make sure it flows with the day.


        p Please include the following information:

